ting longer duration CHeals, whereas we are able to quickly switch to the chanter and fire a Gheal at a moments notice.<br><br>Derringer Labyrinth<br>55 Knight of Pak'Cafan<br>Tarew Marr <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#666666><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub3.ezboard.com/bpaladinsofnorrath.showLocalUserPublicProfile?login=wulfherehausakliufr>Wulfhere Hausakliufr</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FFFFFF>(9/12/00 12:20:16 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub13.ezboard.com/fpaladinsofnorrathtomesofknowledge.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=25.topic&index=20>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://homestead.deja.com/user.marcus_aurelius/files/wulfhere_icon.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> always break mez with taunt first</span><hr size=1> Have all the tanks taunt the mezzed beastie before you attack it. Always do this. It only takes one successful taunt from any melee to prevent it from charging the enchanter. Ifn anyone be too impatient to follow this tactic then give'm a stern lecture on breaking mez.<br><br>Fer ma low/mid 20s groups, ah always have tha enchanter stand well back. Than we melee's all taunt, ah then cast lull until it sticks or ranger/druid casts harmony (irresistable), so now the enchanter be out of reaction range in case all taunts failed, then we attack. Ifn we have a rogue then he starts tha attack with a backstab. The enchanter almost never gets attacked after that 10 or 15 seconds of preparation.<br><br>Breaking Mez be a topic in itself aye. A list o spells and actions that dunnae break mez would be a great boon to many lads. Taunt, Lull, and Harmony ah know for sure but there must be a few others (Snare? Root?) e'en tho Verant nerfed debuffs to aggro. What say ya lads?<br><br>That reminds me, ah need to try addin Root to tha mix. Ah've had it for three full ranks now but forget to cast it at times, from force o habit. N'er forget to root them sow'd gobbos in Runnyeye tho <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br> <p>Wulfhere Hausakliufr<BR>Hammer o Brell, Rallos Zek</p><i></i></td></tr></table><table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top">  Page  <b>1</b> <a href=http://pub13.ezboard.com/fpaladinsofnorrathtomesofknowledge.showMessageRange?topicID=25.topic&start=21&stop=28>2</a> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub13.ezboard.com/fpaladinsofnorrathtomesofknowledge.showMessage?topicID=20.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub13.ezboard.com/fpaladinsofnorrathtomesofknowledge.showMessage?topicID=17.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a href=http://pub13.ezboard.com/fpaladinsofnorrathtomesofknowledge.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=25.topic&index=20><img src=http://eq1.castersrealm.com/pon/images/reply.gif border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub13.ezboard.com/fpaladinsofnorrathtomesofknowledge.emailToFriend?topicID=25.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub13.ezboard.com/fpaladinsofnorrathtomesofknowledge.threadControl?topicID=25.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/professional/deleteThread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands (Moderator only)</a><br> <a href=http://pub13.ezboard.com/fpaladinsofnorrathtomesofknowledge.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=25.topic>Subscribe</a> Click to receive email notification of replies<br>  <a href=http://pub13.ezboard.com/fpaladinsofnorrathtomesofknowledge.unsubscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=25.topic>Unsubscribe</a> Click to stop receiving email notification of replies<br> </td><td align="right" valign="top"></td></tr>